<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>and this person probably just copies the same dps numbers, and didn't even bother to do the math.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
i did the math, in fact i wrote that other post, please show me where i'm wrong? btw, you agreed with me on the other boards and disagree here... odd<br>
<br>
here's my post<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>i chain cast ancient nuke and right click sceptre from rag (1 or 2, i dunno) <br>
<br>
ancient nuke is 1150 + 10% (focus) = 1265 dmg (5.1 seconds) <br>
sceptre is 250 dmg (7 seconds) <br>
<br>
the beauty of a fast r click nuke is it negates the 2.5 refresh time on real spells, so a 7 second r click is really like a 2 second spell. <br>
<br>
this is (1265+250)/(5.1+7)=125 DPS (oops, musta read it wrong earlier) <br>
<br>
now, i can essentially keep this up forever <br>
<br>
with SCM3 max conj spec and 15% mana reducing focus item the 285 mana for my nuke work out to around 157 (45% total savings) mana to cast. or 78 mana per tick (12.1 seconds is close enough to 2 ticks). <br>
<br>
now in POP i have this as my mana regen <br>
<br>
FT 15 <br>
xegony 6 <br>
c3 15 <br>
mental clarity 1 <br>
mor rods 4 <br>
horse medding 22 <br>
<br>
or 63 mana/tick regen <br>
<br>
so essentially chain nuking these 2 in combination i lose 15 mana per tick, with a 4000 mana pool it would take 27 minutes of chain nuking this combo at 125DPS to run oom, a bit of downtime between pulls however and i'll never run oom. <br>
<br>
couple of assumptions, <br>
<br>
1) no resists, i say this is a wash with not taking into account crits (i crit a lot). depending on where you are fighting this might be overstating my dps or understating, but for simplicity call it a wash <br>
<br>
2) c3, i can't cast but i always have it, it lasts a long time and isn't that hard to get. there's also bard song and SP i could have but they aren't common enough to include, i almost always have a mind wracker in group (best friend is a necro) but that's not standard enough to include either <br>
<br>
this is also just with my summoned focus items, there are better ones out there i'm working on getting, if the emperor ever drops his robe for me i can add 5 more mana/tick and there's still more MC and possibly water form i could get and eventually i will<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
braxxus, you say you don't use the bauble, you just use your ODS. magicians get a spell to help increase their long term damage dealing ability and you choose not to use it and then go to the message boards and bitch about your long term DPS... whatever<br>
